---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Ask White Plains
metaDescription: Ask about White Plains neighborhoods, history, events, agendas, community posting, WPCNA, and civic resources using grounded site content.
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Beta</p>
    <h1>Ask White Plains</h1>
    <p>Ask about neighborhoods, history, events, agendas, WPCNA, and community resources.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="ask-shell">
      <div class="ask-panel">
        <div class="ask-intro">
          <span class="tag">Grounded answers</span>
          <p>Answers are based on WPCNA site content and approved local sources. If the assistant cannot find support in those sources, it should say so.</p>
        </div>

        <form
          class="ask-form"
          data-ask-form
          data-api-url="{{ site.askWhitePlainsApiUrl }}"
          data-site-prefix="{{ site.pathPrefix }}"
          novalidate
        >
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="ask-question">Your question</label>
            <textarea
              id="ask-question"
              name="question"
              rows="5"
              maxlength="500"
              placeholder="For example: What does WPCNA do?"
              autocomplete="off"
              required
              data-ask-question
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <p class="ask-helper">
            Ask a specific question about WPCNA, White Plains neighborhoods, local history already covered on the site, meeting materials, community posting, or events.
          </p>

          <div class="ask-actions">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit" data-ask-submit>Ask White Plains</button>
            <p class="ask-meta">Beta: this is not a general-purpose chatbot.</p>
          </div>

          <p class="ask-status" role="status" aria-live="polite" data-ask-status></p>
          <p class="ask-error" role="alert" hidden data-ask-error></p>
          <p class="ask-config" hidden data-ask-config>
            This feature needs an API endpoint before it can answer questions. Set <code>ASK_WHITE_PLAINS_API_URL</code> for the site build after deploying the backend.
          </p>
        </form>

        <section class="ask-results" hidden data-ask-results aria-labelledby="ask-response-heading">
          <div class="section-header ask-results-header">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow">Answer</p>
              <h2 id="ask-response-heading">Response</h2>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ask-answer" data-ask-answer></div>

          <div class="ask-sources" data-ask-sources-wrap hidden>
            <h3>Sources</h3>
            <ul class="ask-source-list" data-ask-sources></ul>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <aside class="detail-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Starter questions</p>
          <h2 class="ask-sidebar-title">Try one of these</h2>
          <div class="starter-list">
            <button class="starter-btn" type="button" data-ask-starter="What does WPCNA do?">What does WPCNA do?</button>
            <button class="starter-btn" type="button" data-ask-starter="How do I submit a community posting?">How do I submit a community posting?</button>
            <button class="starter-btn" type="button" data-ask-starter="Where can I find agendas?">Where can I find agendas?</button>
            <button class="starter-btn" type="button" data-ask-starter="What’s happening in White Plains?">What’s happening in White Plains?</button>
            <button class="starter-btn" type="button" data-ask-starter="What history does the site cover about White Plains?">What history does the site cover about White Plains?</button>
            <button class="starter-btn" type="button" data-ask-starter="Tell me about Fisher Hill.">Tell me about Fisher Hill.</button>
            <button class="starter-btn" type="button" data-ask-starter="How do I learn about forming a neighborhood association?">How do I learn about forming a neighborhood association?</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card" style="margin-top:1.5rem">
          <p class="eyebrow">Scope</p>
          <h3>What this assistant does</h3>
          <ul class="ask-guidelines">
            <li>Answers only from retrieved WPCNA and approved site content, including White Plains history already covered on the site.</li>
            <li>Says when the current sources do not support an answer.</li>
            <li>Keeps responses concise, plainspoken, and source-linked.</li>
            <li>Does not provide legal, medical, emergency, real estate, or official government advice.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script defer src="{{ '/assets/js/ask-white-plains.js' | withPrefix }}"></script>
